<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1762546-wait-i-started-reading-it-but-i-don-t">wait i started reading it but i don&#39;t really get it. There are 12 animal dragon representing different parts of the year cycle. But then there&#39;s another lost mirror dragon, which would make 13 dragons, but it still says 12 dragons, so what?</a>
</div>
