<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/85018580-tom"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1562487651i/85018580._UY100_CR10,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/85018580-tom">Tom</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There are 12 energy dragons, each representing one of the 12 lunar new year animals: snake, horse, goat, monkey, rooster, dog, pig, rat, ox, tiger, ra<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There are 12 energy dragons, each representing one of the 12 lunar new year animals: snake, horse, goat, monkey, rooster, dog, pig, rat, ox, tiger, rabbit, and dragon. The mirror dragon is just another name for the energy dragon representing the dragon. They are the same dragon. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
