<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/451007-i-don-t-get-it-what-was-the-dragons">I don&#39;t get it... What was the dragons name???? She already tried eona while bathing once.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_451007'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2986865-eon">like</a></span>

