<span id="freeTextContainer1012131402411238077">I was really struggling between 1 and 2 stars for this one so I&apos;m compromising with 1.5 stars. </span>
  <span id="freeText1012131402411238077" style="display:none">I was really struggling between 1 and 2 stars for this one so I'm compromising with 1.5 stars. </span>
